data.description:
Showings start 9-15-2023, schedule today, this one won't last!
Priced to sell! A fantastic fixer upper opportunity awaits in this brick ranch style home located in the desirable Pinehurst Estates neighborhood. Situated on a private 10,000 sq. ft. lot, this home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a huge living room that flows into the dining room, and an attached 2 car garage. The large kitchen is open to the great room which hosts a fire place. Go out back to find an attached screened sun room which has a Sauna that will remain. Newer roof, furnace, and a/c. Home has been in the family since it was built in 1974. Tons of potential. Book your showing today!
